# Custom fields

There are a number of custom field types as specified by the <code>field-type</code> attribute.


* __CustomField::Text__   any kind of text

* __CustomField::Email__  valid email address e.g `example@example.com`

* __CustomField::Url__  valid url e.g `https://google.com`

* __CustomField::Phone__ A phone number, can include any values, eg `+46 723 3223 123`

* __CustomField::Date__ Date in  ISO 8601 format e.g `2019-08-28`

* __CustomField::Checkbox__ `true` or `false`

* __CustomField::Number__ any number


